        <briefdescription>
<para>main(args) handles the processing of arguments as sequential actions to pass to the underlying <ref refid="classorg_1_1smallfoot_1_1xpath_1_1XPathTool" kindref="compound">XPathTool</ref>. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>args</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>commandline arguments for processing: <itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>-i loads a file (see <ref refid="classorg_1_1smallfoot_1_1xpath_1_1XPathTool_1a06e5248d8619f00173d9794f30966dc3" kindref="member">XPathTool#load(String)</ref> ) </para></listitem>
<listitem>
<para>-o saves a file (see <ref refid="classorg_1_1smallfoot_1_1xpath_1_1XPathTool_1aa9370fe3a8b0b2d5b91a76190c1599e0" kindref="member">XPathTool#save(String)</ref> ) </para></listitem>
<listitem>
<para>-r sets a replacement value: anything &quot;found&quot; while running a &quot;-f&quot; argument is replaced by this value </para></listitem>
<listitem>
<para>-f starts a search, replacing the value of all matching nodes and attributes with the replacement (-r) value given </para></listitem>
<listitem>
<para>-R sets a replacement pattern: ie /from/to/g : anything &quot;found&quot; while running a &quot;-f&quot; argument, all &quot;from&quot; are replaced by &quot;to&quot;. &quot;g&quot; as the last parameter allows multiple replacements per matching node </para></listitem>
<listitem>
<para>-F starts a search, triggering -R replacement on values on all matching nodes </para></listitem>
<listitem>
<para>-V shows version and quits </para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
<para><xrefsect id="cmdopt_1_cmdopt000001"><xreftitle>Commandline Options</xreftitle><xrefdescription><para>-F execute a search using the replacement already registered: for each matching node, execute the replacement </para></xrefdescription></xrefsect><xrefsect id="cmdopt_1_cmdopt000002"><xreftitle>Commandline Options</xreftitle><xrefdescription><para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">java<sp/>-jar<sp/>xpathtool.jar<sp/>-i<sp/>..<sp/>-r<sp/>..<sp/>-F<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;//ScanTask[@name=&apos;VWVersionSearch&apos;]/@file&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>-o<sp/>..<sp/></highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para></xrefdescription></xrefsect><xrefsect id="cmdopt_1_cmdopt000003"><xreftitle>Commandline Options</xreftitle><xrefdescription><para>The format of the search string is a standard <ulink url="http://www.w3.org/TR/xpath/">XPath</ulink> expression <simplesect kind="see"><para><ulink url="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/XPath">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/XPath</ulink> </para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ulink url="http://www.w3.org/TR/xpath/">http://www.w3.org/TR/xpath/</ulink> </para></simplesect>
</para></xrefdescription></xrefsect></para><para><xrefsect id="cmdopt_1_cmdopt000004"><xreftitle>Commandline Options</xreftitle><xrefdescription><para>-o save an XML file after editing </para></xrefdescription></xrefsect></para><para><xrefsect id="cmdopt_1_cmdopt000005"><xreftitle>Commandline Options</xreftitle><xrefdescription><para>-i read in an XML file for editing </para></xrefdescription></xrefsect></para><para>Always always ALWAYS provide a quick reference and a version output</para><para><xrefsect id="cmdopt_1_cmdopt000006"><xreftitle>Commandline Options</xreftitle><xrefdescription><para>-H Show a simple help screen as a reminder of options which are understood by the application </para></xrefdescription></xrefsect><xrefsect id="cmdopt_1_cmdopt000007"><xreftitle>Commandline Options</xreftitle><xrefdescription><para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">java<sp/>-jar<sp/>xpathtool.jar<sp/>--help<sp/></highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para></xrefdescription></xrefsect></para><para><xrefsect id="cmdopt_1_cmdopt000008"><xreftitle>Commandline Options</xreftitle><xrefdescription><para>-V Show the current release version for reference </para></xrefdescription></xrefsect><xrefsect id="cmdopt_1_cmdopt000009"><xreftitle>Commandline Options</xreftitle><xrefdescription><para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">java<sp/>-jar<sp/>xpathtool.jar<sp/>-V</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.0-20<sp/></highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para></xrefdescription></xrefsect></para><para><xrefsect id="todo_1_todo000001"><xreftitle>Todo</xreftitle><xrefdescription><para>complete usage message </para></xrefdescription></xrefsect></para>        </inbodydescription>
